[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 4.0,
    "text": "This morning we're giving you a crash course in the art of boba."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.0,
    "endTime": 5.0,
    "text": "Boba."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "You probably know it as bubble tea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "Well, the Taiwanese drink is traditionally made of black tea, milk, and boba, those iconic tapioca balls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.0,
    "endTime": 19.0,
    "text": "Well, more coffee and juice shops in the U.S. are introducing the pearls to their drinks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "Joleen Kent met the entrepreneurs helping to bring the boba boom to the U.S."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "In Hayward, California."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "So this is it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "Our U.S. boba factory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "Cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.0,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "At America's first boba factory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.0,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "It smells so good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "You like it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 39.0,
    "text": "That's a brown sugar smell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.0,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "I suited up to see what's behind the bubble tea boom across the country."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "Boba's been in the United States for a long time, and yet production here within the U.S. is still really challenging."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "For boba, you don't have it here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "The only way we can do it is to start everything from scratch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "U.S."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Boba Company was founded by entrepreneurs David Phan, Andrew Chow, and Bing Chen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "They make the iconic chewy balls that make up so many boba drinks here, instead of importing them from Asia."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "Here, the balls that start as tapioca starch get flavored, mixed, and rolled in a tumbler till they're just the right size to fit into those iconic wide straws."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "Oh, there's a big ball."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "Oh, I see the big ball."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "Oh, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "Boba maker in training over here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "See, this is not good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 95.0,
    "text": "So you want to make sure every single boba is the same size so it cooks at the same rate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.0,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "Exactly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "From there, the tapioca balls are sorted into batches, enough for 10,000 cups each."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "Xiexie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "Can I take it home?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.0,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "Why did you start this and go into the boba business more than a decade ago?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "The quick answer is I want a free boba."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "Andrew Chow is also one half of Boba Guys, the national bubble tea chain he co-founded with fellow Taiwanese-American Chen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "I think a lot of founders start a company as a reflection of some hidden or overt part of their identity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "There was maybe a part of us that was like, can we make our culture cool or mainstream or accessible?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.0,
    "endTime": 137.0,
    "text": "This is where the next level of magic happens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.0,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "We're in one of our stores right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "We're going to boil the boba, and you're going to pour that in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "All of it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "There it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 146.0,
    "text": "So we're looking for the equivalent of al dente for boba."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.0,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "Do you want to learn a term?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 149.0,
    "text": "You probably know the term."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "QQ."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "Oh, OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.0,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "What does QQ mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "The chewiness factor?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 156.0,
    "text": "I guess I know this from my Taiwanese background."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.0,
    "endTime": 161.0,
    "text": "Boba first emerged in the 1980s out of tea shops in Taiwan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "All right, we are in Jiuquan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "Chow and Chen traveled there to trace the drink's origins."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "Now, Boba Guys is one of a growing number of companies that's helped bubble tea become a $2.6 billion business in the US alone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.0,
    "endTime": 176.0,
    "text": "I drink boba like every day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.0,
    "endTime": 177.0,
    "text": "I'm addicted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.0,
    "endTime": 179.0,
    "text": "Maybe that's it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.0,
    "endTime": 179.0,
    "text": "Maybe I don't love it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.0,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "Maybe I'm just addicted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.0,
    "endTime": 188.0,
    "text": "According to Yelp, the number of boba cafes across the country has skyrocketed almost 50% over the last few years."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "The taste and the palate of Americans are changing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "Just much more international kind of awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 198.0,
    "text": "And I think that has helped the boba industry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.0,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "What makes a good boba order?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.0,
    "endTime": 206.0,
    "text": "Despite how complex people think it is, it's just boba, milk, tea, and some type of sweetener."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.0,
    "endTime": 207.0,
    "text": "Now we're getting into it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 209.0,
    "text": "We're going to make boba."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.0,
    "endTime": 209.0,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.0,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "So one scoop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.0,
    "endTime": 211.0,
    "text": "Boba first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.0,
    "endTime": 212.0,
    "text": "Yep, boba first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.0,
    "endTime": 215.0,
    "text": "I've been drinking this stuff my entire life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "It's the first time I've ever made it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "There you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.0,
    "endTime": 218.0,
    "text": "It's a little foamy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 220.0,
    "text": "How is the texture?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.0,
    "endTime": 222.0,
    "text": "This is so good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.0,
    "endTime": 222.0,
    "text": "Good?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.0,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "Now, Starbucks is jumping on the bandwagon, saying it'll add pearls inspired by East Asian beverages to some summer drinks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 236.0,
    "text": "We think there's a larger kind of collision course down the road with other cafe styles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.0,
    "endTime": 237.0,
    "text": "Coffee?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.0,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "Maybe coffee, maybe smoothies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 247.0,
    "text": "Do you worry at all with boba becoming so popular that maybe it won't be so closely linked to its Taiwanese roots?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.0,
    "endTime": 249.0,
    "text": "That is always going to be a worry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 250.0,
    "text": "My thing is this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.0,
    "endTime": 253.0,
    "text": "People are learning about Taiwanese culture more than ever before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.0,
    "endTime": 257.0,
    "text": "I think if that's the reason why something becomes mainstream, I think I'm all for it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.0,
    "endTime": 262.0,
    "text": "For CBS Mornings, Jolynn Kent, Hayward, California."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.0,
    "endTime": 265.0,
    "text": "It's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.0,
    "endTime": 266.0,
    "text": "I'll say it's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.0,
    "endTime": 266.0,
    "text": "What do you think?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.0,
    "endTime": 268.0,
    "text": "Strawberry, jasmine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.0,
    "endTime": 270.0,
    "text": "Caught me by surprise, those little jelly bean things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.0,
    "endTime": 271.0,
    "text": "Yeah, they do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.0,
    "endTime": 272.0,
    "text": "They come up and they get you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.0,
    "endTime": 273.0,
    "text": "Yeah, but I like it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.0,
    "endTime": 274.0,
    "text": "It's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.0,
    "endTime": 274.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.0,
    "endTime": 275.0,
    "text": "I really do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.0,
    "endTime": 276.0,
    "text": "It's got a little caffeine in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.0,
    "endTime": 277.0,
    "text": "Give you a little kick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.0,
    "endTime": 278.0,
    "text": "A little bit of kick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.0,
    "endTime": 279.0,
    "text": "It's a great alternative to coffee and tea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.0,
    "endTime": 280.0,
    "text": "I'd maybe do it with a spoon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.0,
    "endTime": 282.0,
    "text": "Can you do that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.0,
    "endTime": 283.0,
    "text": "Yeah, I'm sure you could."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.0,
    "endTime": 284.0,
    "text": "Yeah, people don't recommend it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.0,
    "endTime": 285.0,
    "text": "Yeah, my kids love this stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.0,
    "endTime": 288.0,
    "text": "I see these things all over the place, but I've actually never tried it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.0,
    "endTime": 292.0,
    "text": "You know it's big when Starbucks is like, all right, let's do it too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.0,
    "endTime": 292.0,
    "text": " We're in."
  }
]